{
  "stem": "3382.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were the 10th, 11th, 12th, and 13th, Sunday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We used to sleep in various places, so-called safe houses.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we started on the main-- on the main road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then we went, you know, to side roads.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we cross from one-- from, from the left side of the road, from eastern side of the road to the western side of the road, and again, over zigzagging, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It is how it is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And Sunday, October 13th, we came to Lida.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He dropped-- let me tell you one thing, that on the one, one night, it was the second night that Josef told me, I want from you $500.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Look, I said, you were-- you were there when I offered make-- made-- make a contribution, and Rewenska didn't take it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you want from an AK member take money?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't have $500 with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you should have some money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't tell me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I wouldn't be if I won't give you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, I, I, I can't leave us without money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, so then-- I take away the wagon, go, all right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I was a very-- at the time, quite violent, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know what to hit him, to tell him [NON-ENGLISH] means 'attention' in-- whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then Sula came up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She took out from under somewhere, you know, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a ring with a diamond stone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Look, I said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said that he has no money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it is true.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I have-- I saved this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Take it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He took it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You know, it was a diamond with rubies around.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
